column2: "Maaan, that was so cool! I still dunno if they were Oceanids or whatever, but you got 'em all cleaned up."

"You looked pretty excited to be
neck-deep in danger, huh?
I knew you'd have a good time, killer."
"Too bad I couldn't get out there and show off my own stuff, but I had a great time watchin' you, so thanks!"
"I wish I got this kinda praise from time to time, but fact is, you're the one who deserves it for that kickass show!"
